        "On the one hand, money is a crucial belonging for everyone to embrace, without money, some poor families could not live ahead. Furthermore, there are various types of contributions of wealthy people in society to give a hand to fulfil the demand needed. For example, a lot of donations of materials, food, drink, clothing, and others for the disastrous tsunami in Japan several years ago. Most donations which come from strong capability person due to huge funding are invested in. As a result, the necessities of life are able done by the powerful premium class.",
